      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行将在阿根廷单位出售中录得 10 亿美元税前损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/hsbc-to-book-1-billion-pretax-loss-on-sale-of-argentina-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股有限公司 (HSBC Holdings Plc) 同意出售其在阿根廷的业务，并将在第一季度从此次处置中记入 10 亿美元的费用，因为该银行将重点放在增长更快的亚洲市场上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/hsbc-to-book-1-billion-pretax-loss-on-sale-of-argentina-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 04:40:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
